ZH: 我们必须面对失败，才能更好地成长。
EN: We must face failure in order to grow stronger.

ZH: 他曾多次尝试，但却每次都以失败告终。
EN: He tried multiple times, but each time ended in failure.

ZH: 没有人能永远避免失败。
EN: No one can avoid failure forever.

ZH: 失败并不意味着结束，只是为了更好的开始。
EN: Failure does not mean it's the end, just a better beginning.

ZH: 成功时得意忘形，失败时则是刀光剑影。
EN: Success makes one arrogant, while failure brings hardships.

ZH: 失败教会我们珍惜成功。
EN: Failure teaches us to appreciate success.

ZH: 失败是成功之母。
EN: Failure is the mother of success.

ZH: 面对失败，不如勇敢接受并学习。
EN: Instead of avoiding failure, face it bravely and learn from it.

ZH: 没有人敢断言成功之后就不会有失败。
EN: No one can guarantee there won't be any failure after success.

ZH: 克服失败是变弱为强的秘诀。
EN: Overcoming failure is the key to turning weakness into strength.

ZH: 失败只是一时的，不要让它击垮你。
EN: Failure is only temporary, don't let it defeat you.

ZH: 失败不是终点，也不是终结，只是暂时的停顿。
EN: Failure isn't the end, nor is it the finish, just a temporary pause.

ZH: 失败让人变得更加坚强。
EN: Failure makes people stronger.

ZH: 在失败中寻找成功的契机。
EN: Find opportunities for success in failure.

ZH: 走向成功的路上，总会遇到一些失望和失败。
EN: On the path to success, there will always be disappointments and failures.

ZH: 失败不过是通往成功之路上的一块绊脚石。
EN: Failure is just a stumbling block on the road to success.

ZH: 错误和失败是成功之路上的伴侣。
EN: Mistakes and failures are companions on the road to success.

ZH: 失败并不可怕，就怕失去面对失败的勇气。
EN: Failure is not scary, but losing the courage to face failure is.

ZH: 他没有因为失败而气馁，反而更加努力地奋斗。
EN: He didn't give up because of failure, instead, he worked even harder.

ZH: 生活中，失败是无法避免的，重要的是如何面对并克服。
EN: In life, failure is inevitable, it's important how we face it and overcome it.
